===Etymology===
Modern Greek ''[[σπανακόπιτα]]'', spanakopita, from ''[[σπανάκι]]'', spinach + ''[[πίτα]]'', pie

===Noun===
'''spanakopita''' (''plural'' '''spanakopita''')

#A Greek dish made with pre-cooked [[spinach]], butter, olive oil, [[feta cheese]], [[green onion]]s, [[egg]] and seasoning in [[phyllo pastry]].

====Translations====
*Greek, Modern: [[σπανακόπιτα]] (spanakópita, "spinach pie") ''f'', [[σπανακοτυρόπιτα]] (spanakotyrópita, "spinach-cheese pie") ''f''